sections.History:
===''[[Game of Thrones: A Telltale Games Series]]''===
====&quot;[[The Sword in the Darkness]]&quot;====
When [[Asher Forrester]], [[Beskha]] and [[Malcolm Branfield]] reach [[Meereen]], they meet with [[Croft]] of the [[Second Sons]], who orders his men to apprehend them. Croft gives Asher the choice of losing an eye or a hand, as retribution for stealing from him. Once Asher makes his choice, Croft plunges his knife into the tent support that Asher is pinned to and bursts into laughter. Revealing that he was only playing a joke on them, Croft comments that Asher went as pale as a snow bear's arse.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Sword in the Darkness]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
